<sect2>
<title>Installation of <application>libbonobo</application></title>

<para>Install <application>libbonobo</application> by running the following commands:</para>

<screen><userinput><command>./configure \
--prefix=`pkg-config --variable=prefix ORBit-2.0` \
--sysconfdir=/etc/gnome --libexecdir=`pkg-config \
--variable=prefix ORBit-2.0`/sbin &amp;&amp;
make &amp;&amp;
make install </command></userinput></screen>

</sect2>

